content.p: Assistant Professor, Timetabling Officer, Faculty of Social Sciences Ms Ng Chee Kean is a fellow member of ACCA, UK and a member of MIA, Malaysia. She has about seven years of work experience in public accounting firms. She started teaching in private universities in 2005. Foundation level Undergraduate level Research on financial reporting in Malaysia as well as student experience telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8001
